Title: special_zerto: Error Message in Check_MK HW/SW Inventory
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1705997675
Edition: cre
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0p21

Previously, the agent special_zerto would show the following error message in the Check_MK HW/SW
Inventory

C+:
NOOPParser: Ignoring invalid data b'<<<zerto_agent:sep(0)>>>Initialized OK<<<<host1.example.com>>>>
C-:

Moreover, the service <code>Zerto Agent Status</code> was not discoverable and some piggyback data would
incorrectly be mapped to the source host. This is now fixed.
